            "title": "有片│觀塘地盤集體打鬥  附近街坊：沒有更嘈  只有最嘈",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/30ada1f7ef4371efbb2e97c6360c0102/9923bd03527e49fb8cac0d91875bb598-844f0c531153d3217572372fb0c3bfcd-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b6b28b3e623\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b6b28b3e625\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/81a6bcfda94cf8bc9e739ea6f86fe111/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022012360674994.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（20日）網上流傳兩條影片，觀塘某地盤發生集體打鬥事件，4名地盤工扭作一團，互相拳來腳往，其間有人擸起物件施襲，其他工友合力制止，將兩批人分開。據了解，事件因有工人與管工爭執，爆發混戰。 \n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092295/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩名地盤工圍着一名男子爆粗。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/976ae427a9249fa1b44d9618f8cd33f9/2025-02/11_7.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩名地盤工圍着一名男子爆粗。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092296/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"其他工友勸止。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fcf795c81e18536698dcdab37b6eba71/2025-02/12_3.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        其他工友勸止。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092286/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"先是口角。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d06d1f76ae6238e512a7666878c14508/2025-02/01_3.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        先是口角。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092287/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"繼而動武。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/47b95537ef129d23ef07155acd4d481b/2025-02/02_6.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        繼而動武。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092288/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"四名地盤工扭作一團。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/82c9a957381c3ac6c9354a218d541778/2025-02/03_5.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        四名地盤工扭作一團。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092289/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"四名地盤工扭作一團。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2bd282a3cb9740740b70c49c37e1dc01/2025-02/04_3.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        四名地盤工扭作一團。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092290/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/50a9c2b9308e441789df8e6a7ddd8b6d/2025-02/05_1.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092291/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"工友合力制止。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/387f73e7553b2b15984fe97895d1518d/2025-02/06_1.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        工友合力制止。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092292/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"工友合力制止。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/647d1efc074fdbb89fe1711b2ce472d6/2025-02/07_1.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        工友合力制止。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092293/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"工友將兩批人分開。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/19385fc960190f136b575dfcdc02102a/2025-02/08.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        工友將兩批人分開。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092294/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"工友將兩批人分開。 網片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4e92eb37a78a9d75c124211465c6ba1/2025-02/09.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        工友將兩批人分開。 網片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>事發於今晨11時許，發生在建築地盤天台，第一條短片全長1分17秒，片段一開始即聽到粗口滿天飛，兩男子與一名男子口角，兩名工友在場做和事佬，另一工人則專注倒石屎。 \n\n</p>\n<p>另一片段全長1分43秒，只見四名工人扭作一團，有人擸起金屬板施襲，其他工友將各人拉開，半分鐘後兩批人被隔開，其中一名疑似管工的男人，聽取雙方的不滿，片段結束。 \n\n</p>\n<p>網民表示：「沒有更嘈，只有最嘈」、「住宅樓上樓下都企咗出嚟露台度睇」、「係咪應該報警呢？」、「動口不動手，起碼係君子行為」。 \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
